data.name: gameInstructions.AccessibleDescription
data.value: This label when hovered over can show the player (also known as you!) an image showing a succinct set of instructions telling the player how to play Snaccident Dog. The instructions say: Hello! My name is Snaccident Dog or SD for short. Can you help me eat all of my dog treats? Use those arrow keys on your keyboard to move me towards my food. Please help me become one very happy dog! Also, a group of three dog treats which resemble bones for dogs with a slightly light brown brown colour and a white glimmer on the left appears near the bottom-right corner and has been pointed at with a curved and dotted white arrow. Finally, a hopefully helpful reminder on hiding the instructions by moving the mouse pointer away from this label called 'How do I play?' appears on the bottom-left corner.

data.name: label5.AccessibleDescription
data.value: Snaccident Dog - A hopefully simple and easy-to-play game which may be a little bit stressful at times. Good luck! Special thanks to Moo ICT for inspiring me to make this game. Nathan Tries To Make Games | 2024 - 2025
